<p>So you want to run <%= @distance %>km in <%= @hours%> hours, <%= @minutes %> minutes and <%= @seconds %> seconds eh?</p>

<% if @units == "miles" %>
	<h2>Then set your treadmill to <%= @pace_hour_mph %>mph to hit it - good luck!</h2>
	<p>That's an average pace of <%= @pace_mile_min %>:<%= @pace_mile_sec%> per mile</p>

	<% if @incline > 0 %>
		<p>At an incline of <%= @incline %>% - you will also run up an elevation of <%= @elevation_feet.to_i %> feet! </p>
	<% end %>
<% else %>
	<h2>Then set your treadmill to <%= @pace_hour %>km/h to hit it - good luck!</h2>
	<p>That's an average pace of <%= @pace_km_min %>:<%= @pace_km_sec	%> per km</p>

	<% if @incline > 0 %>
		<p>At an incline of <%= @incline %>% - you will also run up an elevation of <%= @elevation_metres.to_i %> metres! </p>
	<% end %>
<% end %>



